title: I Hid Celebrities In My Instagram Photos For a Week
description:
WATCH MY MUSIC VIDEO: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cV1ecSokIE0

I Hid Celebrities in My Instagram Photos For a Week

I took pictures for my Instagram page and secretly Photoshopped celebrities into the pictures without telling anyone to see if people would notice! I didn't receive the response I necessarily thought I would but what I learned is that you shouldn't focus on your insecurities when uploading photos, because, chances are, no one will notice anyway! This experiment definitely positively impacted my mindset when posting photos of myself! 

I got this idea from Ryan Trahan! WATCH RYAN'S VIDEO: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SSv-wyQXLMQ

description:
30 BENEFITS of Gaining Weight

A lot of people don‚Äôt think about what the BENEFITS of gaining weight are, but there are so many!
